- L1..L6 responsibilities and metrics (MC, CI, φ, Δ_sem)

## 5. Protocols / Protocolos
- Announce/Discover/Connect messages
- STATE_SYNC, EXECUTE_REQUEST, EMERGENCY_SHUTDOWN

## 6. Memory, Runtime, Governance / Memoria, Runtime, Gobernanza
