## 8. Security & Adversarial Defenses / Seguridad y Defensa
- A2.2 detection via Θ(C), quarantine, decoupling strategies

## 9. Tests & Benchmarks / Tests y Benchmarks
- A2.2 harness, L2 drift tests, reproducible lab (Docker + CI)

